</p>
<p>
<seg id="16">Correa specified that the solution of the problem of the shelter granted to Assange since June in Ecuadorian embassy in London, by means of granting a guarantee of inviolability which will allow it to go to Ecuador, is in hands of Great Britain, Sweden and the European judicial authorities and emphasized that there were negotiations in London about search of a solution of the problem of an imprisonment of the founder of WikiLeaks.</seg>
